Array();
}

Why use while loops in your game?
You can use a while loop to run a method or statement over and over.

Your game should be in a method outside of the main, how will you call your game?
You can put a method in a while loop, which will be in the main class.

Why was it reccommended to use .toLowerCase() with your Scanner input?
It is good to use .toLowerCase() because the user's input will not be case sensitive.

